- Jangan diam!  Jawab kami.

00:16:28.680 --> 00:16:29.880
Apa ini?

00:16:30.880 --> 00:16:32.120
Tomat busuk?

00:16:32.200 --> 00:16:36.280
Tomat busuk merusak kari.

00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:38.200
Membawanya keluar!

00:16:40.280 --> 00:16:42.440
[pemutaran musik]

00:16:48.080 --> 00:16:53.160
Kavya, masuklah.

